Skenkings vir Knysna word vroe r vandag op &#8216;n lorrie gelaai beskikbaar gestel deur &#8216;n boer van Oudtshoorn. Foto&#8217;s: Liesel le Roux ______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________Due to the devastating fires in Knysna we would like to assist where possible and we appeal to you to help them with the following items: Blankets Pet Food Tinned food Bottled water Mattresses Any other itemsThese items can be dropped off at Turnberry Boutique Hotel, 130 St John Street, Oudtshoorn before 15:00 today, as the truck will be leaving at 15:00 to take the items to Knysna.